data.name: SchedulerControlVisibleIntervalChanged
data.value: Fires when the time interval represented by the control's scheduling area has been changed.

data.name: SchedulerDeferredScrollingOptionAllow
data.value: Gets or sets whether the deferred scrolling feature is enabled.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsBehaviorMouseWheelScrollAction
data.value: Gets or sets how the mouse wheel scrolling direction is interpreted.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsBehaviorTouchAllowed
data.value: Gets or sets whether the touch device input is analyzed.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsPrintPrintStyle
data.value: Gets or sets the scheduler's printing style.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsRangeControlAllowChangeActiveView
data.value: Gets or sets whether to automatically change the SchedulerControl's active view depending on which time range is selected in the RangeControl.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsRangeControlAutoAdjustMode
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating if the RangeControl should be automatically adjusted after the scheduler visible interval or active view has been changed.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsViewEnableAnimation
data.value: Gets or sets whether a specific animation effect should be applied when an end-user navigates though dates and scrolls resources.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsViewHideSelection
data.value: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the selected time slot remains highlighted when the scheduler control loses focus.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsViewResourceHeaders
data.value: Gets the object which combines appearance options for a scheduler's resource headers.

data.name: SchedulerOptionsViewToolTipVisibility
data.value: Gets or sets the visibility of the scheduler's tooltips.

data.name: SchedulerPrintStyleAppointmentFont
data.value: Gets or sets the font used to print appointments.

data.name: SchedulerPrintStyleHeadingsFont
data.value: Gets or sets the font used to print headings.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsHeight
data.value: Gets or sets the height of the resource header.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsImageAlign
data.value: Gets or sets the image alignment within a resource header.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsImageInterpolationMode
data.value: Gets or sets the algorithm used for image scaling in the headers.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsImageSize
data.value: Gets or sets the size of an image which is shown within a resource header.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsImageSizeMode
data.value: Gets or sets the size mode of an image which is displayed within a resource header.

data.name: SchedulerResourceHeaderOptionsRotateCaption
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether to rotate the caption's text.

data.name: SchedulerStorageAppointmentDependencies
data.value: Gets a storage object which manages dependencies between appointments.

data.name: SchedulerStorageAppointments
data.value: Gets a storage object that contains appointments.

data.name: SchedulerStoragePrepareAppointmentFilterColumn
data.value: Fires when a column, representing an appointment's field, is added to the collection of filter columns contained within the FilterControl.

data.name: SchedulerStoragePrepareResourceFilterColumn
data.value: Fires when a column, representing a resource's field, is added to the collection of filter columns contained within the FilterControl.

data.name: SchedulerStorageResources
data.value: Gets the object which manages resources for appointments.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseAppointmentDisplayOptions
data.value: Provides access to the appointment's display options.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseDateTimeScrollbarVisible
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the date-time scrollbar is visible.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseDisplayName
data.value: Gets or sets the string to display to indicate the scheduler's view.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseEnabled
data.value: Gets or sets if the view is enabled for the SchedulerControl.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseGroupSeparatorWidth
data.value: Gets or sets the width of a separator bar between groups (measured in pixels).

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseMenuCaption
data.value: Gets or sets the menu caption string to indicate the View.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseNavigationButtonAppointmentSearchInterval
data.value: Specifies the time span used to search for appointments by Navigation Buttons.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseNavigationButtonVisibility
data.value: Gets or sets the condition for display of the Navigation Buttons.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseResourcesPerPage
data.value: Gets or sets the number of resources shown at a time on a screen.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseShortDisplayName
data.value: Gets or sets a short name of the current view.

data.name: SchedulerViewBaseShowMoreButtons
data.value: Gets or sets a value which specifies if the More buttons should be shown in the current View.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseAppointmentAutoHeight
data.value: Gets or sets whether an appointment should change its height automatically for the current view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseAppointmentDisplayOptions
data.value: Provides access to the appointment's display options.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseAppointmentHeight
data.value: Gets or sets the height of a single appointment for the current View (in pixels).

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseBounds
data.value: Gets the bounds contained in the view information.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseCellContainers
data.value: Provides access to visible time cells in the current View.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseGroupSeparators
data.value: Gets the group separators settings.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseNavigationButtons
data.value: Provides access to the Navigation Buttons collection of the current view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBasePaintAppearance
data.value: Gets the appearance settings applied to the current scheduler view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseResourceHeaders
data.value: Gets the resource headers currently shown in the current scheduler view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseView
data.value: Gets the current scheduler view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseVisibleIntervals
data.value: Gets the visible intervals of the current view.

data.name: SchedulerViewInfoBaseVisibleResources
data.value: Gets a collection of visible resources for the current view.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryDayView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Day View.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryFullWeekView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Full Week View.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryGanttView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Gantt view.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryMonthView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Month View.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryTimelineView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Timeline View.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryWeekView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Week View.

data.name: SchedulerViewRepositoryWorkWeekView
data.value: Gets an object that defines the settings of the scheduler's Work Week View.

data.name: StorageBindedImageComboBoxEditStorage
data.value: Gets or sets the SchedulerStorage object that contains appointments and resources to fill an editor.

data.name: TimeCellEndOfHour
data.value: Determines if the cell border is drawn with a darker color.

data.name: TimeCellIsWorkTime
data.value: Determines if the cell belongs to the working time range and should be colored accordingly.

data.name: TimeIndicatorDisplayOptionsShowOverAppointment
data.value: Gets or sets whether the Time Indicator is displayed over appointments in the view.

data.name: TimelineViewAppearance
data.value: Provides access to the properties that control the appearance of the TimelineView's elements.

data.name: TimelineViewAppointmentDisplayOptions
data.value: Provides access to the Timeline View appointments display options.

data.name: TimelineViewCellsAutoHeightOptions
data.value: Provides access to options for specifying cell auto height behavior in the Timeline or Gantt view.

data.name: TimelineViewDeferredScrolling
data.value: Provides access to parameters that control deferred scrolling.

data.name: TimelineViewOptionsSelectionBehavior
data.value: Provides access to properties which specify how the time cell selection changes when the Timeline scale is changed.

data.name: TimelineViewScales
data.value: Provides access to a collection of time scales displayed in the Timeline view.

data.name: TimelineViewSelectionBar
data.value: Provides access to the selection bar options.

data.name: TimelineViewShowResourceHeaders
data.value: Gets or sets whether resource headers are displayed.

data.name: TimelineViewTimelineScrollBarVisible
data.value: Specifies whether a vertical row scrollbar is visible, and the vertical scrolling is enabled in rows of the Timeline view grouped by resource.

data.name: TimelineViewWorkTime
data.value: Gets or sets the work time interval for a Timeline View.

data.name: TimeZoneEditEditorTypeName
data.value: Gets the class name of the editor.

data.name: TimeZoneEditProperties
data.value: Gets an object that contains settings specific to the editor.

data.name: VerticalResourceHeaderRotateCaption
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether to rotate the caption's text.

data.name: WeekDaysCheckEditFirstDayOfWeek
data.value: Gets or sets the day which starts the WeekDaysCheckEdit control's week.

data.name: WeekDaysCheckEditUseAbbreviatedDayNames
data.value: Specifies whether the control displays short names of week days .

data.name: WeekDaysCheckEditVisibleWeekDays
data.value: Gets or sets days of the week visible in the WeekDaysCheckEdit control.

data.name: WeekDaysCheckEditWeekDays
data.value: Gets or sets the day of the week or a specific group of days that is selected in the editor.

data.name: WeekDaysCheckEditWeekDaysChanged
data.value: Fires when the control's weekday checkbox changes its state.

data.name: WeekDaysEditEditorTypeName
data.value: Gets the class name of the editor.

data.name: WeekDaysEditProperties
data.value: Gets an object that contains settings specific to the editor.

data.name: WeeklyRecurrenceControlFirstDayOfWeek
data.value: Gets or sets the day which starts the WeeklyRecurrenceControl's week.

data.name: WeekOfMonthEditEditorTypeName
data.value: Gets the class name of the editor.

data.name: WeekOfMonthEditProperties
data.value: Gets an object that contains settings specific to the editor.

data.name: WeekViewAppearance
data.value: Provides access to the properties that control the appearance of the WeekView's elements.

data.name: WeekViewAppearanceCellHeaderCaption
data.value: Gets the appearance settings used to paint a day cell's header within the Week or Month View.

data.name: WeekViewAppearanceCellHeaderCaptionLine
data.value: Gets the appearance settings used to paint the line at the bottom of a day cell's header within the Week or Month View.

data.name: WeekViewAppearanceTodayCellHeaderCaption
data.value: Gets the appearance settings used to paint the header of the day cell representing the current date within the Week or Month View.

data.name: WeekViewAppearanceTodayCellHeaderCaptionLine
data.value: Gets the appearance settings used to paint the line at the bottom of the today cell's header within the Week or Month View.

data.name: WeekViewAppointmentDisplayOptions
data.value: Provides access to the appointment's display options pertaining to the Week View.

data.name: WeekViewDeferredScrolling
data.value: Provides access to parameters that control deferred scrolling.

data.name: WorkWeekViewAppearance
data.value: Provides access to the properties that control the appearance of the WorkWeekView's elements.

data.name: WorkWeekViewShowFullWeek
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether this view should show all the days of the week.
